Description:
   Reach Remedy is a Cipher field medicine technique. The operative has
   trained to rapidly neutralize toxins and poisons using a compact kit of
   antidotes always kept within easy reach. When deployed, the Reach Remedy
   removes poison effects from the Cipher without requiring them to leave
   combat or seek outside assistance.

   The technique reflects the Cipher's professional preparation for
   operating in environments where they may be subjected to poisons —
   whether from enemy casters, trapped objects, or poisoned weapons. The
   remedies are applied rapidly enough that the Cipher can detoxify
   mid-combat. More advanced toxins may require a full dose of the kit
   and cannot be countered by partial application.
